
Ques 04:Restaurant Menu Order System

Project Overview
----------------
Develop a Spring Core application to create food order objects dynamically using Factory Design Pattern.

Requirements

The application should support menu items with prices:

Pizza — ₹250
Burger — ₹150
Biryani — ₹300

Factory should create the selected food order object and calculate bill amount.

Flow
Customer selects food item
Factory creates matching order object
Order preparation starts
Final bill amount is displayed